'''白三烯C4合酶'''（{{lang-en|Leukotriene C4 synthase}}）是一种由人类基因''LTC4S''编码的[[酶|酶]]。<ref name="pmid8052639">{{cite journal | author = Lam BK, Penrose JF, Freeman GJ, Austen KF | title = Expression cloning of a cDNA for human leukotriene C4 synthase, an integral membrane protein conjugating reduced glutathione to leukotriene A4 | journal = Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A | volume = 91 | issue = 16 | pages = 7663–7 | pmid = 8052639 | pmc = 44462 | doi =10.1073/pnas.91.16.7663  |date=Sep 1994}}</ref><ref name="entrez">{{cite web | title = Entrez Gene: LTC4S leukotriene C4 synthase| url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=gene&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=4056| accessdate = }}</ref>

该蛋白也简称为'''LTC4S'''（或称为'''谷胱苷肽S-转移酶II'''，{{lang-en|glutathione S-transferase II}}）是一种将[[白三烯A4|白三烯A4]]和[[谷胱甘肽|谷胱甘肽]]结合生成[[白三烯C4|白三烯C4]]的[[合酶|合酶]]。它也是[[跨膜蛋白|跨膜蛋白]][[MAPEG家族|MAPEG家族]]的一员。

